      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 id="federal-deadlines" class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-6">Major Federal Grant Deadlines: Q1 2026</h2>
    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
