      <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do I need to be fully released from the CAF to apply?</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700">Most VAC benefits require you to be released, but programs like Prince's Trust Canada often welcome transitioning members who are still serving but preparing for release.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-4">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I use the Education Benefit for any business course?</h3>
